  "projectType": "api-service",
  "projectName": "Ask Nova API",
  "projectDescription": "A FastAPI-powered AI support chatbot backend for SoftSUITE Novo, using RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) with LanceDB, HuggingFace embeddings, and Groq LLM to answer questions from a document knowledge base.",
